 his research group is currently involved in projects at both poles including the wais divide drilling project in antarctica and the neem ice core in greenland tags air quality antarctica and the arctic carbon dioxide climate change energy geochemistry glacial geochronology ice cores methane oceans & coasts paleoclimate public health 2012 leopold leadership program the stanford woods institute for the environment stanford university stanford ca 94305
